data.description: Extremely spacious 4 bedroom 2 bathroom tri-level home. On the main level you step into a tiled living room area that opens up to a nice breakfast bar, kitchen & large walk-in pantry. The main level also has the primary bedroom & bathroom. Downstairs is a large finished basement that could be used as 5th bedroom &/or an enormous family room. Above the basement there are 3 guest bedrooms & 1 bathroom. Downstairs off the primary bedroom there is a large finished & insulated carpeted garage with a separate entry door to the backyard. Washer & dryer convey. This room provides lots of dry storage or if you add a ductless ac it would be perfect as another bonus room/6th bedroom! The possibilities are endless with this home! Gorgeous fenced-in backyard with a firepit & a sundeck. Fantastic central location with a close commute to downtown, the beaches, & very close to UNF, FSCJ & all the shopping & restaurants the St. Johns Town Center has to offer.
